# Rerere Cache Directory
# This directory stores git rerere (reuse recorded resolution) entries.
# It is used by the release workflow to automatically resolve known conflicts.
#
# To update this cache after resolving conflicts locally:
#   1. Run ./scripts/ghoten-resolve.sh
#   2. Resolve any conflicts manually
#   3. The script will update this directory
#   4. Commit and push: git add .rerere-cache/ && git commit -m "chore: update rerere cache"
#
# See: https://git-scm.com/docs/git-rerere
